  "detailed_description": "After years of watching Earth with envious eyes, the Martians have finally invaded and are launching their attack from their base on the dark side of the moon.<br><br>You are the Jetman, a cyborg with enough firepower to take on the alien threat.<br><br>Strap on your jetpack and set a course for the moon.<br><br>You'll need all your skills and dexterity to overcome the enemy and destroy the alien threat once and for all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/03b7d3fdc77f8b7f119b90b687531c4a.poster.avif?t=1727888492\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/03b7d3fdc77f8b7f119b90b687531c4a.webm?t=1727888492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/03b7d3fdc77f8b7f119b90b687531c4a.mp4?t=1727888492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tA game in the spirit of 80's and 90's arcade and console shoot-em-ups, created by fans of the genre.<br></li><li>\tA single mission with plenty of extra objectives to boost scores and status.<br></li><li>\tHigh-score Leaderboards to lay down the challenge to other players.<br></li><li>\tSoundtrack by renowned musician Barry Leitch.<br></li><li>\tMaximize your score on your run through, complete objectives, find the secret bonuses, and rescue stranded astronauts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/402340e8b1ec4cb584aef863f919e458.poster.avif?t=1727888492\" width=120 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/402340e8b1ec4cb584aef863f919e458.webm?t=1727888492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/402340e8b1ec4cb584aef863f919e458.mp4?t=1727888492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hey pilot! Yes, you there!<br>Visit our website (over on the right) to play a free web demo!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "After years of watching Earth with envious eyes, the Martians have finally invaded and are launching their attack from their base on the dark side of the moon.<br><br>You are the Jetman, a cyborg with enough firepower to take on the alien threat.<br><br>Strap on your jetpack and set a course for the moon.<br><br>You'll need all your skills and dexterity to overcome the enemy and destroy the alien threat once and for all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/03b7d3fdc77f8b7f119b90b687531c4a.poster.avif?t=1727888492\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/03b7d3fdc77f8b7f119b90b687531c4a.webm?t=1727888492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/03b7d3fdc77f8b7f119b90b687531c4a.mp4?t=1727888492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tA game in the spirit of 80's and 90's arcade and console shoot-em-ups, created by fans of the genre.<br></li><li>\tA single mission with plenty of extra objectives to boost scores and status.<br></li><li>\tHigh-score Leaderboards to lay down the challenge to other players.<br></li><li>\tSoundtrack by renowned musician Barry Leitch.<br></li><li>\tMaximize your score on your run through, complete objectives, find the secret bonuses, and rescue stranded astronauts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/402340e8b1ec4cb584aef863f919e458.poster.avif?t=1727888492\" width=120 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980190/extras/402340e8b1ec4cb584aef863f919e458.w